## Data Sources

Both datasets are sourced from Kenneth French's Data Library:
- Fama/French 3 Factors (monthly) — save as `data_ff3.csv`
- 49 Industry Portfolios (monthly) — save as `data_ind49.csv`

Download from: https://mba.tuck.dartmouth.edu/pages/faculty/ken.french/data_library.html

Place both files in the `/data` folder before running the notebook.

---

